We’re planning to redo our deck this year— it’s in pretty bad shape and our patio furniture was looking equally as rough. It was such an eyesore I couldn’t take it any longer. I teamed up with @joann_stores and found the most perfect outdoor fabrics from @richloomfabrics which is stain, water, and fade resistant. With two kids and two dogs that’s a requirement. I ended up recovering the existing foam to save money and we’ve spent every sunny day out here since! #sponsored #handmadewithjoann #joannpartner #outdoorfurniture
